{"tid":646943,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"千等萬待！白箱《SHIROBAKO》劇場版製作決定  原文網址: 千等萬待！白箱《SHIROBAKO》劇場版製作決定","createTime":"2018-04-29T12:58:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-29T13:07:50.000Z","uid":2566,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8221e15b3fdd5cde52995fe38763ab5c3799ce40","tid":646943,"uid":2566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:58:48.000Z","msg":"記者羅仁豪／東京報導<br />\n經典職場動畫《SHIROBAKO》，動畫公司 P.A.WORK 在今日公開了將製作劇場版動畫的消息，完結至今已過了3年多的時間，萬眾矚目的新作企劃總算開始進行，喵森學《勇往直前》 主角仁王站立的宣傳圖也一同上架。<br />\n《SHIROBAKO》（中譯：白箱）是 P.A.WORK 職場女孩系列原創動畫的第二部作品，影射日本動畫業界的真人真事為腳本去改編製作，內容提及了許多動畫界知識與瑣事趣聞，標題的「SHIROBAKO」，則是意指作品播放前發送給所有工作人員的未剪接樣本，因為都裝在白色的CD盒裡面才有此說。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3255/3255015.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3255%2F3255015.jpg&h=ec0c35d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原文網址: 千等萬待！白箱《SHIROBAKO》劇場版製作決定 | ETtoday遊戲雲 | ETtoday新聞雲 手機版 MobileWeb <a href=\"https://game.ettoday.net/article/1159497.htm#ixzz5E48w358K\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgame.ettoday.net%2Farticle%2F1159497.htm%23ixzz5E48w358K&d=AXSC5AwpE0WKf1GhavFs9ZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=80afbc64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://game.ettoday.net/article/1159497.htm#ixzz5E48w358K</a> <br />\nFollow us: @ETtodaynet on Twitter | ETtoday on Facebook"},{"pid":"f4789ed88368b46c8e9ee7191a534ed688271a65","tid":646943,"uid":8307,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T12:59:11.000Z","msg":"又wow"},{"pid":"9ad688410864d090f6aeb3da3c4a8660af64a800","tid":646943,"uid":33651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:00:29.000Z","msg":"點樣呀"},{"pid":"3aba4a456fde1635c3400cb4d92adce6867a0486","tid":646943,"uid":37890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-29T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"第3個<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed77b7212de4db00f9635b